posting_body: ['VIEW OUR WEBSITE:', '<URL>', 'M Street apartments offer many ways to connect, relax and recharge offering everything from a state-of-the-art fitness center to an amazing clubhouse.', 'Come by today for a tour!', 'Copy and Paste this link to view our screening criteria:', '<URL>', 'This studio apartment features a modern gourmet kitchen with dishwasher, microwave and garbage disposal.', 'This Studio also features a full wall of windows to allow all the natural light in!', 'Have a lot of clothes?', 'No problem!', 'Your huge walk in closet will take care of that!', 'This apartment requires a $325 deposit.', 'M Street, managed by Holland Residential', '910 8th Avenue', 'Seattle, WA 98104', 'show contact info', 'Apartment Features', '* Linen Closet', '* Disposal', '* Whirlpool Appliances', '* Pantry', '* Walk-in Closet', '* Private Patio or Private Balcony (on select apartments)', '* Wood-Like Floors', '* Quartz Countertops', '* Refrigerator, Microwave, Dishwasher & Electric Stove', '* Central Heat and Air', '* Designer Track Lighting', '* Extra Storage', '* Stainless Steel Appliances', '* Ceiling Fan', '* Full sized Washer and Dryer in unit']
